data.title: Outfits
data.meta_description: Outfits are sets of clothes for the Beheaded. They are unlocked by finding their blueprints and unlocking them from the Collector with cells like all other upgrades or items.

Why did it have to be snakemen?[ap] Finish a run without taking any trap damage N/A Knight's Outfit An exotic armor from another universe[aq] Found in a loreroom in the Prisoners' Quarters 1 Commando Outfit ..and so he left, with everything but his humanity[ar] Kill the two shadow imps that spawn from the random altar in biomes N/A Familiar Outfit Datamining this would be really meta[as] Drop an item into lava (done by entering the Cavern Key door in Prisoners' Quarters, then dropping the backpacked item and using the Homunculus Rune to throw it into the lava) N/A Ironclad Outfit Its previous wearer sold their soul in exchange for demonic powers.[at] Collect 3 keys, the Emerald Key is from an elite room, the Sapphire Key is from a choice altar in a biome and the Ruby Key is from a shop.

Can be collected over multiple Biomes.
